to begin there. And I'm just going to take

00:00:59.960 --> 00:01:14.290
my scissors and I left a little space where
I marked it to help me guide to give a straight

00:01:14.290 --> 00:01:38.280
line. I'm just going to go all the way down.
Like that. Now my excess is still pinned to

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:51.600
the actual side that I want and that's fine.
