00:01:58.720 --> 00:02:10.789
a little snippet, then I can take my pin out
and follow the guide to the next pin. So I

00:02:10.789 --> 00:02:19.920
can have a pretty nice straight line. And
if you're working with new fabric, it's pretty

00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:38.049
stiff so you can probably get a straight cut.
